author: 13abc
title: Perrysburg releases new renderings of Riverside Park
text:
Related Documents Riverside Park - 2015-10-13 PERRYSBURG, Ohio (13abc Actions) - The City of Perrysburg has released new renderings of Riverside Park.
City leaders showed the documents at a meeting last night.
In the plans, the city outlines the different kinds of materials they'd like to use, as well as close-up pictures of certain parts of the park.
There are also outlines of a bike bath and a walkway.
To be clear, these plans are not finalized.
A city council member tells 13abc that the final vote is expected by the end of the year.
